EThis%20post%20originally%20appeared%20in%20the%20Business%20Insider%20Today%20newsletter.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20sign%20up%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Finsider-today%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20daily%20newsletter%20here%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpenAI%20wants%20to%20control%20the%20narrative.%20Literally.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20giant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-acquires-tbpn-tech-talk-show-in-media-push-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebought%20TBPN%2C%20the%20tech%20industry's%20hottest%20talk%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20a%20deal%20so%20shocking%20that%20one%20of%20its%20hosts%20joked%20it%20wasn't%20a%20belated%20April%20Fool's%20joke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20good%20chunk%20of%20you%20might%20be%20asking%2C%3Cem%3E%20%26quot%3BTBP%20what%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20You're%20not%20wrong%20for%20wondering.%20As%20popular%20as%20the%20weekday%2C%20three-hour%20show%20is%2C%20it's%20also%20intensely%20focused%20on%20tech.%20(That's%20on%20purpose.%20John%20Coogan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20cohosts%2C%20recently%20talked%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fjacoogan_if-tbpn-hits-10m-subscribers-something-has-activity-7435760962135212032-eHlA%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETBPN%20being%20intentionally%20niche%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20that%20specific%20group%2C%20it%20is%20huge.%20Dubbed%20%26quot%3BSportsCenter%26quot%3B%20for%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20it's%20basically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftbpn-dove-deep-sportscenter-silicon-valley-tech-bros-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20must-watch%20for%20tech%20bros%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hence%20why%20people%20are%20freaking%20out%20about%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20tech%20startups%20buying%20one%20of%20the%20industry's%20most%20popular%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI's%20Peter%20Kafka%20has%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-openai-bought-tbpn-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat%20analysis%20on%20why%20the%20deal%20makes%20sense%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20a%20company%20that's%20thinking%20in%20%3Cem%3Etrillions%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20dollars%2C%20spending%20a%20few%20hundred%20million%20(terms%20weren't%20disclosed%2C%20but%20that's%20the%20number%20being%20floated)%20to%20nab%20your%20industry's%20most%20influential%20show%20makes%20a%20lot%20of%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20just%20getting%20a%20show.%20It's%20a%20direct%20line%20to%20the%20people%20shaping%20the%20industry%20it's%20looking%20to%20dominate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(We've%20also%20got%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-tbpn-deal-what-people-are-saying-silicon-valley-altman-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20more%20takes%20on%20the%20news%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20other%20smart%20people%20around%20the%20interwebs.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuestions%20are%20swirling%20about%20whether%20this%20OpenAI-version%20of%20TBPN%20can%20retain%20its%20magic.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETBPN%20hosts%20Coogan%20and%20Jordi%20Hays%20have%20said%20they%20will%20maintain%20editorial%20independence%20from%20OpenAI.%20But%20TBPN%20will%20also%20assist%20OpenAI%20with%20marketing%20and%20communications%20outside%20the%20show%2C%20potentially%20blurring%20the%20lines%20between%20coverage%20and%20promotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it's%20not%20like%20TBPN%20is%20looking%20to%20break%20big%20scoops%20or%20investigations%20like%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes.%26quot%3B%20Coogan%20and%20Hays%20are%20both%20former%20tech%20founders%20who%20are%20unabashedly%20pro-tech.%20That%20formula%20has%20helped%20them%20court%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20is%20unlikely%20to%20change%20under%20the%20new%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20%3Cem%3Ewill%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20is%20how%20many%20of%20those%20big%20names%20are%20willing%20to%20come%20on%20now%20that%20the%20show%20is%20backed%20by%20their%20competition.%20Will%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20welcome%20TBPN%20back%20to%20Meta's%20headquarters%20now%20that%20his%20rival%20Sam%20Altman%20is%20signing%20their%20checks%3F%20What%20about%20executives%20from%20Anthropic%20or%20Google%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20competitors%20will%20need%20to%20ask%20themselves%3A%20Is%20reaching%20the%20audience%20TBPN%20holds%20worth%20helping%20a%20rival%20you're%20actively%20fighting%20for%20market%20share%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20seem%20inevitable%20is%20that%20we're%20about%20to%20get%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fget-ready-for-wave-of-tbpn-clones-post-openai-deal-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20LOT%20of%20TBPN%20copycats%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20writes%20BI's%20Sydney%20Bradley%2C%20Dan%20Whateley%2C%20and%20Lucia%20Moses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELivestreaming%20talk%20shows%20were%20already%20on%20the%20rise.%20OpenAI%20shelling%20out%20for%20TBPN%20only%20adds%20fuel%20to%20that%20fire.%20And%20in%20an%20industry%20known%20for%20imitation%2C%20other%20AI%20giants%20might%20snap%20up%20their%20own%20version%20of%20TBPN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20influx%20of%20new%20shows%20could%20just%20water%20down%20the%20market%2C%20though.%20SportsCenter%20was%20largely%20successful%20because%20it%20was%20the%20only%20place%20to%20watch%20sports%20highlights.%20That%20changed%20with%20social%20media%2C%20and%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20end%20of%20SportsCenter's%20era%20of%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETBPN%20may%20be%20at%20the%20center%20of%20tech%20conversation%20right%20now.%20The%20question%20is%20how%20long%20any%20one%20show%20can%20stay%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-openai-competitors-still-go-on-tbpn-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775220104000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cfb437e762ed6cfe449f9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-openai-competitors-still-go-on-tbpn-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI's%20purchase%20of%20TBPN%20sparks%20debate%20on%20tech%20industry%20influence.%20TBPN%20hosts%20vow%20independence%2C%20but%20will%20competitors%20still%20engage%20with%20the%20show%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ddefrancesco%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20DeFrancesco)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-openai-competitors-still-go-on-tbpn-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Microsoft%20released%203%20new%20AI%20models%2C%20ramping%20up%20competition%20with%20its%20close%20partner%2C%20OpenAI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Microsoft%20logo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cf9bfbe762ed6cfe449f20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EZamek%2FVIEWpress%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMicrosoft%20has%20made%20three%20new%20in-house-built%20AI%20models%20available%20on%20its%20Foundry%20platform.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20company%20reducing%20its%20reliance%20on%20its%20longtime%20partner%2C%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20deal%20agreed%20in%20October%20allowed%20Microsoft%20more%20independence%20from%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20has%20released%20three%20AI%20models%20created%20in-house%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20a%20move%20that%20signals%20a%20push%20toward%20greater%20independence%20from%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-openai-equity-stake-early-bet-openai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elongtime%20partner%2C%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMAI-Transcribe-1%2C%20MAI-Voice-1%2C%20and%20MAI-Image-2%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20designed%20for%20transcription%2C%20voice%20generation%2C%20and%20image%20creation%20%E2%80%94%20are%20exclusively%20available%20on%20Microsoft's%20Foundry%20platform%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcommunity.microsoft.com%2Fblog%2Fazure-ai-foundry-blog%2Fintroducing-mai-transcribe-1-mai-voice-1-and-mai-image-2-in-microsoft-foundry%2F4507787%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20Foundry%20is%20a%20platform%20within%20Microsoft%20Azure%2C%20which%20allows%20developers%20and%20businesses%20to%20purchase%2C%20build%2C%20and%20customize%20AI%20applications%20using%20a%20range%20of%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20models%20are%20available%20to%20enterprise%20customers%2C%20putting%20them%20in%20direct%20competition%20with%20similar%20tools%20from%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20offers%20Whisper%20for%20transcription%2C%20text-to-speech%20models%20for%20voice%2C%20and%20DALL%C2%B7E%20for%20image%20generation.%20All%20three%20are%20also%20available%20on%20Foundry%2C%20either%20as%20individual%20products%20or%20as%20part%20of%20OpenAI's%20broader%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMAI-Transcribe-1%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20accurate%20transcription%20model%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20and%20MAI-Voice-1%20%26quot%3Bsets%20a%20new%20standard%20for%20natural%20speech%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mustafa%20Suleyman%2C%20CEO%20of%20Microsoft%20AI%2C%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmustafasuleyman%2Fstatus%2F2039704624006148195%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20is%20OpenAI's%20largest%20investor%2C%20and%20the%20two%20companies%20remain%20close%20partners.%20OpenAI%20relies%20on%20Microsoft's%20Azure%20cloud%20service%20to%20train%20and%20run%20its%20models%2C%20while%20Microsoft%20uses%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20to%20power%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternal-audio-microsoft-copilot-confusion-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECopilot%2C%20its%20AI%20chatbot%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Microsoft%20has%20increasingly%20been%20staking%20its%20own%20claim%20in%20the%20AI%20race%2C%20reducing%20its%20reliance%20on%20OpenAI%20by%20building%20its%20own%20frontier%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20Suleyman%20formed%20a%20superintelligence%20team%20at%20Microsoft%20focused%20on%20training%20%26quot%3Bfrontier%20models%20of%20all%20scales%20with%20our%20own%20data%20and%20compute%20at%20the%20state-of-the-art%20level%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20the%20company%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-ceo-mustafa-suleyman-agi-evolving-openai-relationship-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eself-sufficient%20in%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrevious%20agreements%20between%20the%20two%20companies%20have%20shaped%20how%20independently%20Microsoft%20can%20develop%20advanced%20AI%20systems.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-completes-restructuring-for-profit-signs-new-microsoft-agreement-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enew%20deal%20announced%20in%20October%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20allowed%20the%20companies%20to%20%26quot%3Bindependently%20pursue%20AGI%20(artificial%20general%20intelligence)%20alone%20or%20in%20partnership%20with%20third%20parties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-models-azure-mai-transcribe-voice-image-foundry-openai-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22