Fzendaya-las-vegas-wedding-chapel-the-drama-promotion%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enewlyweds%20at%20a%20Las%20Vegas%20chapel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20popping%20up%20in%20New%20York%20City%20to%20foot%20the%20bill%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.them.us%2Fstory%2Fzendaya-bought-a-lesbian-bride-her-wedding-dress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebride-to-be's%20dream%20gown%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20all%20in%20hopes%20of%20luring%20audiences%20to%20theaters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20something%20more%20sinister%20was%20brewing%20beneath%20the%20press%20tour's%20sunnier%20surface.%20Much%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffilm%2F2026%2Fmar%2F25%2Fthe-twist-in-robert-pattinson-zendaya-romcom-the-drama%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emovie's%20central%20twist%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20tests%20a%20seemingly%20perfect%20couple's%20relationship%20after%20one%20half%20makes%20a%20shocking%20admission%20in%20the%20week%20leading%20up%20to%20their%20wedding%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Drama%26quot%3B%20got%20some%20eleventh-hour%20backlash%20of%20its%20own%20in%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20its%20April%203%20premiere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20breathless%20speculation%20on%20Reddit%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20movie's%20twist%2C%20a%20report%20from%20TMZ%20threatened%20to%20not%20only%20spoil%20the%20movie%2C%20but%20bring%20its%20upbeat%20press%20tour%20to%20a%20screeching%20halt%3A%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tmz.com%2F2026%2F03%2F24%2Fzendaya-the-drama-called-out-by-columbine-parent%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efather%20of%20a%20Columbine%20victim%3C%2Fa%3E%20broadly%20condemned%20the%20movie%2C%20telling%20the%20tabloid%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bdisgusted%26quot%3B%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20movie%20that%20compels%20parents%20of%20mass%20shooting%20victims%20to%20speak%20out%20is%20clearly%20dealing%20with%20provocative%20subject%20matter%20%E2%80%94%20IndieWire%20film%20critic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2Fcriticism%2Fmovies%2Fthe-drama-movie-review-robert-pattinson-zendaya-1235186011%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid%20Ehrlich%20described%20%26quot%3BThe%20Drama%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20movie%20that's%20%26quot%3Beager%20to%20stick%20out%20its%20tongue%20and%20lick%20one%20of%20the%20last%20genuine%20third%20rails%20of%20American%20discourse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F6zmKcUa4Xxk%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Drama%20%7C%20Official%20Trailer%20HD%20%7C%20A24%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20it%20didn't%20take%20long%20for%20that%20discourse%20to%20devolve%20even%20before%20the%20movie%20hit%20theaters.%20Online%2C%20commenters%20who%20read%20spoilers%20or%20guessed%20what%20the%20movie%20must%20entail%20were%20eager%20to%20moralize%20scenes%20they'd%20yet%20to%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20finding%20out%20what%20Emma's%20secret%20is%20I%20don't%20think%20I'll%20watch%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fspoilers%2Fcomments%2F1qvgsae%2Fmajor_spoilers_below_for_the_drama%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20user%20wrote%20on%20Reddit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20referring%20to%20Zendaya's%20character.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20it's%20trying%20to%20justify%20something%20really%20bad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20the%20counter%20campaign%20to%20create%20drama%20around%20%26quot%3BThe%20Drama%26quot%3B%20was%20in%20full%20swing.%20Reddit%20dug%20up%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fmovies%2Fmovie-news%2Fdrama-director-kristoffer-borglis-age-gap-1236548464%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2012%20essay%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20Drama%26quot%3B%20director%20Kristoffer%20Borgli%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20for%20a%20local%20Norwegian%20magazine%20about%20the%20May-December%20romance%20he%20had%20with%20a%20younger%20girl%20while%20in%20his%2020s.%20Commenters%20online%20were%20soon%20swearing%20up%20and%20down%20that%20the%20movie%20was%20reprehensible%20both%20for%20its%20rumored%20plot%20points%20and%20the%20alleged%20misdeeds%20of%20its%20director%2C%20all%20before%20any%20of%20them%20could%20have%20seen%20a%20single%20frame%20of%20it%20outside%20of%20clips%20from%20the%20trailer.%20(A24%20and%20Borgli%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20far%20from%20the%20first%20to%20point%20out%20that%20in%20a%20highly%20competitive%20attention%20economy%2C%20blind%20outrage%20feels%20much%20more%20satisfying%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-explains-news-gen-zers-improve-media-literacy-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emedia%20literacy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20the%20way%20the%20internet%20has%20already%20reduced%20%26quot%3BThe%20Drama%26quot%3B%20to%20its%20shocking%20twist%20misses%20the%20point%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarning%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe're%20about%20to%20get%20into%20true%20spoiler%20territory%2C%20so%20if%20you%20haven't%20seen%20the%20movie%20yet%2C%20now's%20your%20chance%20to%20stop%20reading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bb02c437-1593-444c-8f1e-73da29db3655%5C%22%3E'The%20Drama'%20isn't%20actually%20about%20its%20disturbing%20twist%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20about%20relationship%20dynamics%20and%20the%20price%20of%20devotion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222902%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mamoudou%20Athie%20and%20Alana%20Haim%20as%20Mike%20and%20Rachel%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Drama.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cc0b376a864f6fcd7bc01a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221924%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMamoudou%20Athie%20and%20Alana%20Haim%20as%20Mike%20and%20Rachel%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Drama.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EA24%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Drama%2C%26quot%3B%20written%20and%20directed%20by%20Borgli%2C%20follows%20engaged%20couple%20Charlie%20(Pattinson)%20and%20Emma%20(Zendaya)%20in%20the%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20their%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20night%2C%20while%20drinking%20wine%20with%20their%20married%20friends%2C%20Mike%20(Mamoudou%20Athie)%20and%20Rachel%20(Haim)%2C%20the%20foursome%20drunkenly%20decide%20to%20go%20around%20the%20table%20and%20reveal%20the%20worst%20thing%20they've%20ever%20done.%20Stories%20of%20romantic%20strife%2C%20adolescent%20cruelty%2C%20and%20cyber-bullying%20ensue%2C%20but%20Emma's%20reveal%20is%20a%20doozy.%20She%20says%20that%20as%20a%20tween%2C%20she%20had%20fantasies%20of%20killing%20her%20classmates%20in%20a%20mass%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Charlie%20tries%20to%20laugh%20it%20off%2C%20assuming%20his%20beautiful%20fianc%C3%A9e%20must%20be%20joking%2C%20Emma%20doubles%20down%3A%20She%20stole%20her%20dad's%20gun%20and%20brought%20it%20to%20school%2C%20she%20says.%20She%20went%20deaf%20in%20one%20ear%20because%20she%20was%20practicing%20her%20aim%20in%20the%20woods%20and%20held%20the%20gun%20too%20close%20to%20her%20face.%20This%20was%20no%20fleeting%20whim%2C%20although%2C%20crucially%2C%20she%20didn't%20end%20up%20going%20through%20with%20her%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tense%2020-minute%20scene%20is%20the%20movie's%20turning%20point%20and%20plot%20engine%2C%20which%20kick-starts%20Charlie's%20increasingly%20frenzied%20existential%20crisis.%20He%20begins%20hallucinating%20a%20rifle%20in%20Emma's%20hands%2C%20imagining%20worst-case%20scenarios.%20As%20a%20British%20expat%2C%20he%20clings%20to%20their%20cultural%20divide%20to%20explain%20Emma's%20pre-pubescent%20compulsion%3A%20It's%20not%20like%20it%20was%20an%20original%20idea%2C%20he%20reasons%20in%20desperation.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcssh.northeastern.edu%2Fsccj%2Fmass-killing-database%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMass%20shootings%20happen%20in%20the%20US%20all%20the%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20his%20spiral%20continues%2C%20Charlie's%20reaction%20reveals%20just%20as%20much%20about%20him%20as%20Emma's%20secret%20does%20about%20her.%20He's%20a%20posh%20guy%2C%20preoccupied%20with%20keeping%20up%20appearances.%20He%20didn't%20grow%20up%20as%20Emma%20did%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ostracized%20Black%20girl%20in%20Louisiana%20%E2%80%94%20and%20as%20much%20as%20she%20tries%20to%20explain%20her%20thought%20process%2C%20how%20she's%20changed%20and%20grown%2C%20he%20simply%20wasn't%20there.%20He%20can%20only%20take%20her%20word%20for%20it%2C%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20reality%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Drama%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20a%20movie%20about%20gun%20violence%20or%20school%20shootings%2C%20because%20this%20dichotomy%20holds%20fast%20no%20matter%20what%20Emma's%20secret%20is.%20Charlie%20will%20never%20know%20for%20sure%20what%20Emma%20is%20thinking%2C%20nor%20vice%20versa.%20Whether%20you%20agree%20or%20disagree%20with%20making%20an%20aborted%20mass%20shooting%20the%20twist%20of%20a%20black%20comedy%2C%20the%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20the%20details%20are%20only%20important%20because%20they%20represent%20one%20of%20the%20few%20universally%20reprehensible%20things%20a%20person%20could%20reveal%20that%20would%20provoke%20such%20stark%20a%20moral%20dilemma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20dilemma%20is%20what%20allows%20%26quot%3BThe%20Drama%26quot%3B%20to%20pose%20big%20questions%20about%20love%20and%20its%20necessary%20enigmas%3A%20How%20much%20mystery%20can%20we%20endure%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20happily%20ever%20after%3F%20What%20does%20unconditional%20love%20actually%20look%20like%3F%20How%20much%20of%20any%20relationship%20is%20projection%20and%20perception%2C%20rather%20than%20seeing%20a%20partner%20for%20who%20they%20really%20are%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Drama%26quot%3B%20doesn't%20answer%20these%20questions%2C%20but%20posing%20them%20is%20powerful%20enough.%20There%20are%20no%20answers%20%E2%80%94%20only%20complicated%20people%20trying%20their%20best%20to%20understand%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20wouldn't%20get%20any%20of%20that%20nuance%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bostonglobe.com%2F2026%2F03%2F31%2Farts%2Fthe-drama-robert-pattinson-zendaya%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erage-bait%20headlines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20of%20course.%20Those%20invite%20immediate%20and%20definitive%20moral%20judgment%2C%20which%20is%20ironic%2C%20since%20that%20impulse%20is%20exactly%20what%20Charlie%20and%20Emma%20spend%20the%20entire%20movie%20struggling%20to%20overcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-drama-movie-twist-spoilers-backlash-columbine-zendaya-robert-pattinson-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775217842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cee9c6c02a678bd7e47968%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-drama-movie-twist-spoilers-backlash-columbine-zendaya-robert-pattinson-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A24's%20buzzy%20new%20dark%20comedy%20%26quot%3BThe%20Drama%26quot%3B%20stars%20Robert%20Pattinson%20and%20Zendaya%20as%20an%20engaged%20couple.%20Its%20plot%20twist%20has%20sparked%20backlash%20online.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cahlgrim%40insider.com%20(Callie%20Ahlgrim)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-drama-movie-twist-spoilers-backlash-columbine-zendaya-robert-pattinson-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20spent%2048%20hours%20in%20Chicago%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20left%20with