0frozen%20lake%20with%20a%20pathway%20and%20buildings%20on%20the%20left%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6f3a38373a547629c7409%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20visit%20any%20city%2C%20I%20like%20to%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20walking%20around%20outside%20to%20get%20the%20lay%20of%20the%20land.%20So%20when%20I%20was%20exploring%20parks%20in%20downtown%20Chicago%20on%20a%20freezing%20day%20in%20February%2C%20with%20a%20stiff%20face%2C%20frigid%20fingertips%2C%20and%20cracked%20lips%2C%20I%20thought%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20my%20first%20trip%20to%20Chicago%20was%20a%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20fresh%20snow%20sparkled%20and%20the%20icy%20lake%20was%20mesmerizingly%20beautiful%2C%20I%20should%20have%20picked%20a%20warmer%20season%20for%20my%20first%20trip%20to%20this%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESince%20I%20visited%20in%20winter%2C%20I%20should%20have%20explored%20indoor%20spaces%2C%20such%20as%20museums%20and%20libraries.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20park%20in%20Chicago%20with%20snow%20and%20trees%20lining%20either%20side%20of%20a%20concrete%20path%20and%20buildings%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd34c4c02a678bd7e46e9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20let%20the%20weather%20stop%20me%20from%20spending%20my%20days%20outside%20exploring%20neighborhoods%20and%20parks.%20I%20even%20went%20to%20the%20beach.%20This%20ended%20up%20being%20a%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20enjoyed%20getting%20to%20know%20the%20city%20on%20foot%2C%20I%20couldn't%20help%20thinking%20all%20of%20these%20places%20would%20have%20