luxury.%20I%20booked%20a%20Spa%20King%20Guestroom%20for%20one%20night%20for%20%24240.%20It%20was%20a%20corner%20room%20on%20the%2016th%20floor%20with%20floor-to-ceiling%20windows%20on%20every%20exterior%20wall.%20Asymmetrical%20mirrors%2C%20cartoonish%20light%20fixtures%2C%20and%20mismatched%20nightstands%20made%20my%20stay%20feel%20unique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20taking%20a%20bath%20in%20the%20large%20soaking%20tub%20with%20a%20view%20of%20downtown%20Chicago%2C%20I%20felt%20more%20wrapped%20in%20luxury%20than%20I%20have%20in%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffour-seasons-seattle-room-review-tour%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%241%2C000-a-night%20hotel%20rooms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I%20was%20bummed%20I%20only%20booked%20one%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFor%20such%20a%20short%20trip%2C%20I%20should%20have%20focused%20on%20one%20neighborhood%20rather%20than%20covering%20more%20ground.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20street%20in%20downtown%20Chicago%20viewed%20from%20above%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6f453f573a637a7567147%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20explored%20a%20few%20Chicago%20neighborhoods%20along%20the%20coast%2C%20from%20the%20Loop%20to%20Hyde%20Park.%20I%20also%20spent%20a%20morning%20strolling%20the%20nearby%20town%20of%20Kenilworth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20I%20packed%20too%20many%20locations%20into%20this%2048-hour%20trip.%20Instead%20of%20scratching%20the%20surface%20in%20all%20these%20places%2C%20I%20wish%20I'd%20stuck%20to%20just%20one%20neighborhood%20and%20gotten%20to%20know%20it%20as%20deeply%20as%20possible.%20Next%20time%2C%20I%20will.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchicag