20mixed%20emotions%3A%20relief%2C%20sadness%2C%20and%20the%20sudden%20realization%20that%20I%20wasn't%20getting%20any%20younger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20ignited%20something%20in%20me%2C%20and%20that's%20how%20I%20found%20myself%20staring%20out%20at%20a%20seemingly%20endless%20line%20of%20buoys%20floating%20in%20the%20freezing%20cold%20Brazos%20River%20in%20Waco%2C%20Texas%2C%20about%20to%20compete%20in%20a%20half-Ironman%20%E2%80%94%20a%20feat%20I%20was%20intent%20on%20completing%20before%20I%20turned%2050.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f7513f62-445a-441e-9108-ca9ab114dd57%5C%22%3ETraining%20for%20a%20half-Ironman%20was%20ambitious%2C%20especially%20since%20I%20couldn't%20swim%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bonny%20Osterhage%20on%20bike%20during%20endurance%20race%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bc00bfebc245a53a811d06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20did%20my%20half-Ironman%20in%20Waco%2C%20Texas.%3Cp%3EBonny%20Osterhage%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I've%20always%20been%20active%20%E2%80%94%20mixing%20aerobics%2C%20running%2C%20step%20class%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-training-kim-kardashian-changed-my-view-of-fitness-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrength%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Zumba%2C%20and%20cycling%20%E2%80%94%20I%20never%20considered%20myself%20an%20athlete.%20That%20changed%20during%20my%20midlife%20meltdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20generally%20subscribes%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bgo%20big%20or%20go%20home%26quot%3B%20mentality%2C%20I%20decided%20I%20wanted%20to%20tackle%20the%2070.3-mile%20challenge%20before%20my%20half-century%20birthday.%20There%20were%20two%20glaring%20hurdles%20between%20me%20and%20that%20finish%20line%3A%20First%2C%20I%20had%20less%20than%20a%20year%20to%20train%2C%20and%20second%20(and%20most%20important)%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-learned-to-swim-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20swim%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20run%20half-marathons%20and%20embarked%20on%20150-mile%20bike%20rides%20with%20gusto%2C%20but%20the%201.2-mile%20swim%20would%20be%20an%20issue.%20I%20could%20stay%20afloat%20without%20panic%2C%20but%20properly%20swimming%20for%20long%20distances%3F%20That%20wasn't%20in%20my%20wheelhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20successful%2C%20I'd%20need%20to%20double%20down%20on%20my%20efforts.%20With%20just%20over%20seven%20months%20until%20the%20race%2C%20I%20hired%20a%20coach%2C%20followed%20a%20plan%2C%20and%20trained%20for%20two%20to%20four%20hours%20a%20day%20(outside%20of%20my%20physically%20demanding%20job%20as%20a%20fitness%20instructor%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foptimize-workout-personal-trainer-red-green-flags-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonal%20trainer%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20intense%2C%20and%20there%20were%20days%20I%20seriously%20doubted%20myself%2C%20but%20I%20stuck%20to%20the%20training%20schedule%2C%20fueled%20my%20body%20properly%2C%20and%20prioritized%20rest%20days%20and%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e527d5e-460f-41a0-89a2-fa0e0ad6c494%5C%22%3EI%20nearly%20gave%20up%20on%20race%20day%20but%20ultimately%20crossed%20the%20finish%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20race%2C%20I%20nearly%20choked%20ahead%20of%20the%201.2-mile%20swim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20stripped%20off%20my%20wetsuit%2C%20about%20to%20give%20up%20everything%20I'd%20worked%20so%20hard%20for%2C%20my%20husband%20offered%20me%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finspirational-quotes-from-super-successful-people-2016-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewords%20of%20encouragement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%20how%20to%20do%20this%2C%20you've%20worked%20hard%2C%20and%20you%20are%20more%20than%20capable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20go%20do%20it!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20zipped%20my%20suit%20back%20up%20and%20got%20back%20in%20line%20with%20the%20other%20swimmers%2C%20ready%20to%20take%20the%20plunge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeven%20hours%20later%2C%20I%20heard%20the%20words%20I'd%20been%20training%20to%20hear%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20a%20half-Ironman%20finisher.%26quot%3B%20I%20knew%20then%20that%20the%20way%20I%20viewed%20midlife%2C%20and%20my%20life%20in%20general%2C%20had%20been%20changed%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224654099f-4356-4e7b-b4ae-f763f8383d48%5C%22%3EThe%20race%20empowered%20me%20physically%20and%20mentally%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222785%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bonny%20Osterhage%20and%20partner%20on%20the%20beach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bc031cd387710cb9e4632e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222089%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20friends%20and%20family%20were%20supportive%20throughout%20my%20training%20journey.%3Cp%3EBonny%20Osterhage%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20physical%20progress%20I%20made%20during%20training%20was%20great.%20My%20journey%20catapulted%20me%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-tell-if-youre-actually-fit-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20physical%20shape%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20felt%20and%20looked%20strong%20and%20healthy.%20However%2C%20the%20real%20rewards%20weren't%20visible%20to%20the%20naked%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20of%20empowerment%20I%20felt%20from%20following%20through%20on%20a%20commitment%20to%20myself%20and%20doing%20something%20that%2C%20up%20until%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20had%20seemed%20impossible%20was%20life-changing.%20I%20learned%20to%20listen%20to%20myself%20and%20ignore%20the%20negative%20voices%20in%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20made%20me%20as%20strong%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20stronger%20%E2%80%94%20mentally%20than%20I%20was%20physically%20and%20allowed%20me%20to%20reconnect%20with%20myself%20in%20a%20way%20that%20I%20hadn't%20in%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e66711c2-ab55-4ee1-a005-593c138ba21a%5C%22%3EMy%20experience%20made%20me%20wish%20more%20women%20tried%20endurance%20sports%20in%20midlife%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mental%20benefits%20I%20reaped%20are%20the%20reason%20I%20wish%20more%20women%20would%20take%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhardest-endurance-races-in-the-world-2017-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendurance%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20midlife%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20suggesting%20that%20every%20woman%20in%20her%2050s%20needs%20to%20tackle%20a%20half-Ironman%2C%20but%20distance%20sports%20of%20all%20types%20and%20levels%20require%20people%20to%20show%20up%20for%20themselves%2C%20believe%20in%20themselves%2C%20and%20push%20themselves.%20It's%20in%20those%20moments%20of%20discomfort%20that%20they%20learn%20who%20they%20are%20and%20what%20they're%20made%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20my%20half-Ironman%2C%20I%20walked%20away%20with%20the%20understanding%20that%20aging%20isn't%20optional%2C%20but%20how%20well%20I%20do%20it%20is.%20Life%20is%20the%20biggest%20endurance%20event%20of%20all.%20How%20I%20train%20for%20it%20matters%2C%20and%20it's%20never%20too%20late%20to%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-shape-by-50-changed-workout-endurance-sports-training-ironman-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775217721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bc129bd387710cb9e463da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-shape-by-50-changed-workout-endurance-s