%20mercenary%20to%20kill%20him%20back%20in%202015.%20He%20said%20it%20was%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20effort%20by%20the%20UAE%20to%20eliminate%20people%20who%20opposed%20them%20politically.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-ex-soldiers-accused-of-running-uaes-secret-assassination-squad-report-11307006%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-ex-soldiers-accused-of-running-uaes-secret-assassination-squad-report-11307006%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-ex-soldiers-accused-of-running-uaes-secret-assassination-squad-report-11307006%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20bought%20a%20house%20that's%20too%20small%20so%20we%20could%20afford%20our%20dream%20neighborhood.%20A%20%24300%2C000%20third-party%20loan%20will%20help%20us%20renovate.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20posing%20for%20a%20picture%20in%20front%20of%20a%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd5bddc02a678bd7e4704e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDerek%20and%20Kate%20Feinberg%20bought%20a%20small%20home%20in%20a%20neighborhood%20they%20loved%20and%20plan%20to%20renovate%20using%20a%20third-party%20loan.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Derek%20and%20Kate%20Feinberg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDerek%20and%20Kate%20Feinberg%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20Wayne%2C%20Pa.%2C%20but%20couldn't%20afford%20a%20big%20enough%20home%20there.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20bought%20a%20smaller%20home%20in%20the%20location%20they%20wanted%2C%20and%20plan%20to%20renovate%20it%20instead.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20used%20a%20platform%20that%20allows%20them%20to%20borrow%20money%20based%20on%20the%20post-renovation%20value%20of%20their%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Derek%20Feinberg%2C%2041%2C%20and%20Kate%20Feinberg%2C%2038.%20The%20couple%20purchased%20a%20small%20home%20in%20Wayne%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20expand%20immediately.%20With%20little%20equity%2C%20they%20used%20RenoFi%2C%20a%20financing%20platform%20that%20allows%20borrowers%20to%20secure%20a%20loan%20based%20on%20a%20property's%20future%20value.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20never%20thought%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fwhat-to-look-for-when-buying-a-house%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewe'd%20be%20homeowners%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20I%20thought%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuying-home-renting-better-worse-zillow-how-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewe'd%20be%20renters%20forever%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20I%20woke%20up%20one%20day%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20buy%20a%20house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20renting%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-suburbs-in-the-us-ranked%235-ardmore-pennsylvania-16%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eapartment%20in%20Ardmore%2C%20Pennsylvania%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20we%20were%20looking%20there%20and%20in%20the%20surrounding%20towns%20in%20the%20area.%20Wayne%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20was%20a%20pipe%20dream.%20It's%20beautiful%2C%20but%20it%20is%20very%20pricey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDerek%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It's%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20wealthier%2C%20well-known%20towns.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20beautiful%20neighborhoods%20of%20suburban%20Philadelphia%20popping%20up%20off%20the%20main%20line%2C%20and%20Wayne's%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20stumbled%20across%20an%20open%20house%20one%20day%2C%20and%20I%20sent%20Derek's%20parents%20to%20go%20look%20at%20it%2C%20and%20they%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20come%20see%20this%20house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ended%20up%20buying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20shot%20of%20Haverford%2C%20a%20town%20in%20Delaware%20County%2C%20Pennsylvania.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd5fb56a864f6fcd7bc6e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20aerial%20view%20of%20Wayne's%20Delaware%20County%20neighbor%20Haverford%2C%20Pennsylvania.%3Cp%3Ehalbergman%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EImmediately%2C%20my%20first%20thought%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20house%20is%20too%20small.%20It's%20not%20going%20to%20work.%20We%20can't%20do%20this.%26quot%3B%20But%20after%20some%20convincing%2C%20I%20realized%20you%20can't%20relocate%20your%20house.%20So%20we%20bought%20this%20property%20because%20of%20its%20location.%20You%20just%20can't%20beat%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20Derek%20promise%20me%20that%20if%20we%20were%20buying%20this%20house%2C%20then%20we%20would%20do%20an%20addition%20within%20five%20years.%20We%20started%20a%20little%20bit%20sooner%20than%20five%20years%2C%20but%20after%20living%20in%20the%20home%2C%20I%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%20bigger%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20move%20because%20I%20love%20our%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b75c68d0-4236-4193-b270-cb9b0f2a8015%5C%22%3EOur%20home%20was%20priced%20well%20below%20others%20in%20the%20neighborhood%2C%20but%20it's%20small%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20There%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20houses%20going%20over%20asking%20in%20the%20area.%20We%20had%20to%20go%20well%20above%20asking%20to%20get%20this%20house%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbought-house-good-rate-feel-trapped-mortgage-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einterest%20rates%20weren't%20great%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20they%20were%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20when%20everyone%20got%20those%203.5%25%20interest%20rates.%20It%20probably%20wasn't%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-now-could-be-good-time-to-buy-house-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20time%20to%20buy%20a%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20we%20did%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20closed%20on%20the%20house%20in%20November%202022%20for%20%24420%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20comparison%2C%20the%20median%20home%20price%20in%20our%20neighborhood%20is%20somewhere%20around%20%241%20million.%20%3Cem%3E%5BAccording%20to%20Realtor.com%2C%20the%20median%20listing%20price%20in%20Wayne%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20was%20%241%2C050%2C000%20in%20March%202026.%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDerek%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20remember%20our%20bid%20for%20the%20house%20actually%20wasn't%20the%20highest%2C%20but%20I%20think%20the%20owner%20knew%20we%20were%20going%20to%20be%20living%20there%20and%20knew%20that%20the%20people%20above%20us%20were%20basically%20buying%20the%20house%20as%20an%20investment%20project%20to%20either%20rent%20it%20out%20or%20knock%20it%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20owner%20wanted%20someone%20to%20continue%20living%20there%20and%20occupying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20bought%20it%20as%20a%20three-bedroom%2C%20one-bath%20with%20about%201%2C100%20square%20feet%2C%20a%20large%20fenced-in%20backyard%2C%20and%20a%20beautiful%20porch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20house%20was%20so%20small%20and%20had%20three%20very%20tiny%20bedrooms%2C%20we%20actually%20had%20to%20cut%20down%20a%20wall%20between%20two%20of%20the%20adjoining%20bedrooms%20because%20our%20bed%20wouldn't%20fit%20in%20any%20of%20the%20rooms.%20So%20now%2C%20before%20the%20renovation%20starts%2C%20it's%20actually%20a%20two-bedroom%2C%20one-bath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20kind%20of%20laissez-faire%20about%20the%20whole%20thing%20because%20we%20didn't%20have%20these%20ideas%20of%20what%20we%20wanted%3B%20we%20just%20knew%20we%20wanted%20more%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20of%20a%20white%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd5bddc02a678bd7e4704d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Feinberg's%20home%20in%20Wayne%2C%20Pennsylvania.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Derek%20and%20Kate%20Feinberg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20addition%20will%20be%20adding%20about%20700%20square%20feet%20onto%20our%20home%20at%20the%20back%2C%20blowing%20out%20the%20back%2C%20and%20adding%20a%20big%20open%20living%20space%2C%20a%20big%20open%20kitchen%2C%20a%20big%20living%20room%2C%20two%20more%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20another%20bedroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20only%20time%20we're%20doing%20an%20addition%2C%20so%20it's%20just%20all%20in%2C%20basically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f4cb81d9-7575-44bb-8f31-40cce4ed385b%5C%22%3EWe%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20much%20our%20renovations%20would%20cost%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20we%20bought%20the%20house%2C%20we%20knew%20we%20were%20going%20to%20put%20an%20addition%20on%20it.%20In%20my%20head%2C%20I'm%20thinking%2C%20an%20addition%20is%20going%20to%20cost%2C%20what%2C%20%24100%2C000%3F%20It's%20going%20to%20be%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20doing%20research%20and%20talking%20to%20people%20who%20are%20experts%20in%20this%20field%2C%20we%20discovered%20that%20that's%20not%20the%20case%2C%20and%20it's%20way%2C%20way%20more%20expensive%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20constantly%20running%20the%20numbers%2C%20comparing%20our%20equity%20and%20how%20much%20the%20project%20is%20going%20to%20cost%20and%20all%20of%20these%20things%2C%20and%20discovered%20I%20didn't%20think%20there%20was%20any%20way%20that%20we%20could%20financially%20do%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDerek%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20just%20didn't%20have%20any%20idea%20how%20much%20things%20would%20cost%20until%20we%20started%20talking%20to%20people%20who%20have%20done%20stuff%20like%20this.%20Then%20you're%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20crap%2C%20we%20may%20have%20to%20wait%20a%20little%20longer%20or%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20borrow%20from%20our%20family%20or%20something.%26quot%3B%20That%20was%20not%20something%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20called%20my%20personal%20bank%20and%20another%20credit%20union%20a%20family%20member%20had%20used%2C%20ran%20some%20numbers%2C%20and%20realized%20that%20number's%20not%20going%20to%20cut%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDerek%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20was%20talking%20to%20some%20friends%20about%20it%2C%20and%20one%20mentioned%20that%20his%20friend%20does%20this%20thing%20called%20a%20construction%20loan%20with%20this%20company%2C%20RenoFi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20something%20that%20we%20never%20even%20considered%2C%20that%20a%20company%20would%20consider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-jersey-home-renovation-kitchen-remodel-garage-addition-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20value%20post-renovation%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20what%20they%20would%20give%20you%20in%20a%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20submitted%20our%20plans%20for%20our%20house%2C%20and%20they%20sent%20out%20an%20appraiser%20to%20our%20home.%20They%20appraised%20the%20value%20of%20our%20home%20now%2C%20and%20then%20they%20would%20develop%20what%20they%20think%20the%20house%20will%20be%20worth%20post-renovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20value%20was%20around%20%24600%2C000%2C%20and%20the%20estimated%20appraisal%20post-renovation%20is%20a%20little%20over%20%241%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20loan%20that%20we%20got%20with%20RenoFi%20was%20%24300%2C000%2C%20and%20the%20amount%20that%20we%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20get%20through%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-helocs-work-borrower-shares-experience-costs-interest-rates-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econventional%20HELOC%20loan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20just%20going%20off%20the%20current%20value%20of%20our%20home%2C%20probably%20would%20have%20been%20somewhere%20around%20%24175%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20great%20option%20for%20us%20because%20instead%20of%20having%20this%20little%20amount%20in%20equity%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20lot%20in%20equity%20because%20it's%20taking%20into%20account%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDerek%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20numbers%20kind%20of%20made%20the%20decision%20for%20us.%20We%20could%20have%20bought%20a%20different%20house%20in%20a%20less%20desirable%20location.%20But%20every%20time%20we%20went%20and%20checked%20something%20out%2C%20it%20just%20confirmed%20to%20us%20that%20the%20move%20was%20to%20renovate%20a%20smaller%20home%20in%20our%20ideal%20neighborhood%2C%20because%20we%20were%20never%20finding%20what%20we%20wanted%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20did%20explore%20renovating%20versus%20buying%20a%20new%20home%2C%20but%20we%20love%20Wayne.%20We%20love%20our%20community.%20We%20love%20the%20walkability%20of%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20if%20we%20wanted%20to%20get%20a%20home%20of%20the%20size%20we%20would%20get%20with%20our%20renovation%2C%20the%20price%20is%20astronomical%20%E2%80%94%20we'd%20be%20priced%20out%20of%20our%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbought-smaller-home-better-location-renovate-third-party-loan-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775217061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd6767c02a678bd7e470e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%2