%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20tracked%20my%20daily%20protein%2C%20fiber%2C%20and%20calorie%20intake%20using%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMost%20of%20the%20advice%20was%20helpful%2C%20and%20I%20tweaked%20some%20of%20my%20eating%20habits.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20I%20found%20some%20of%20the%20advice%20nitpicky%20and%20annoyingly%20worded.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20never%20stick%20to%20food-tracking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flost-75-pounds-via-app-created-ai-powered-digital-twin-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweight%20loss%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20than%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20quickly%20get%20frustrated%20when%20I%20couldn't%20find%20the%20exact%20product%20on%20the%20app's%20database%20or%20recall%20the%20portion%20size%20I%20consumed%2C%20which%20is%20important%20when%20tracking%20every%20calorie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20over%20time%2C%20as%20my%20knowledge%20of%20nutrition%20developed%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20didn't%20want%20to%20just%20focus%20on%20calorie%20restriction%20or%20fat%20loss.%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20build%20muscle%20mass%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-eat-enough-protein-without-skimping-on-fiber-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeat%20more%20fiber%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20wasn't%20the%20primary%20goal%20of%20the%20apps%20I%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20tried%20using%20ChatGPT%20to%20track%20my%20protein%2C%20fiber%2C%20and%20calorie%20intake%20for%20two%20weeks.%20I%20hoped%20it%20would%20be%20better%20at%20recognizing%20larger%20patterns%20in%20my%20eating%20habits%2C%20which%20could%20help%20me%20tweak%20my%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%2C%20I%20typed%20everything%20I%20ate%20and%20drank%20into%20the%20same%20chat%20conversation.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20included%20the%20estimated%20amounts%2C%20brands%20when%20applicable%2C%20and%20specific%20restaurants%20I%20visited.%20It%20felt%20easier%20to%20dump%20everything%20into%20one%20chat%20instead%20of%20searching%20for%20each%20individual%20product%20like%20I%20did%20on%20food-tracking%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20included%20how%20many%20calories%20I%20burned%20in%20my%20Orangetheory%20classes%20(as%20estimated%20by%20a%20heart%20rate%20monitor%20I%20wore%20in%20class)%2C%20how%20many%20steps%20I%20walked%2C%20and%20how%20many%20calories%20I%20burn%20at%20rest%2C%20which%20I%20learned%20from%20my%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-lost-fat-changed-body-composition-in-1-year-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebody%20composition%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221532%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ChatGPT%20analyzing%20diet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2d32da96e437d6eb832b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22688%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20tried%20to%20get%20as%20specific%20as%20possible%2C%20listing%20brands%20when%20it%20felt%20relevant.%3Cp%3EChatGPT%2FJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20the%20only%20one%20using%20AI%20to%20fine-tune%20my%20diet.%20Lately%2C%20Shannon%20O'Meara%2C%20a%20registered%20dietitian%20at%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOrlando%20Health%2C%20a%20healthcare%20organization%20in%20Florida%2C%20has%20seen%20patients%20use%20AI%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-moms-use-ai-co-parent-kids-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhip%20up%20recipes%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebased%20on%20what's%20in%20their%20fridge%20or%20within%20their%20budgets.%20I%20asked%20her%20to%20help%20me%20assess%20how%20helpful%20ChatGPT's%20advice%20was%2C%20and%20if%20she'd%20recommended%20using%20it%20for%20diet%20tips%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20positive%20aspects%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20noting%20that%2C%20as%20with%20any%20AI-related%20task%2C%20how%20you%20interact%20with%20the%20technology%20determines%20the%20results.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20only%20going%20to%20get%20out%20what%20you%20put%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20two%20weeks%2C%20I%20got%20better%20at%20choosing%20protein-rich%20meals%2C%20which%20helped%20me%20stay%20fuller%20without%20relying%20on%20empty%20calories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20where%20AI%20was%20useful%2C%20and%20where%20it%20fell%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2256ea7867-0d6e-452a-8fec-246fd191d444%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20gave%20sound%20advice%20on%20sneaking%20more%20protein%20into%20my%20diet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Grain%20bowl%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2d38ca7a4f9df67ba391d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAdding%20nuts%20to%20meals%20is%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20get%20more%20protein.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20advice%20a%20Life%20Time%20trainer%20gave%20me%20in%20January%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20helping%20me%20build%20muscle%20mass%20and%20lose%20fat%2C%20I'd%20been%20aiming%20to%20consume%20between%2090%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-eat-100-grams-protein-a-day-dietitian-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E100%20grams%20of%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20day%2C%20particularly%20on%20the%20three%20to%20four%20days%20per%20week%20that%20I%20work%20out.%20I'd%20consume%20a%20full%20scoop%20of%20protein%20powder%20and%20eat%20meal-prepped%2C%20protein-forward%20dinners%2C%20but%20still%20struggled%20to%20hit%20the%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tended%20to%20drop%20off%20on%20rest%20days%2C%20omitting%20the%20protein%20powder%20because%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20consume%20more%20ultra-processed%20food%20than%20I%20had%20to.%20Those%20were%20days%20I%20was%20also%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%20or%20going%20out%20after%20work%2C%20where%20I%20could%20lose%20track%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommon-mistake-equation-calculating-protein-goal-needs-weight-loss-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprotein%20goals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20advised%20aiming%20for%20at%20least%2080%20grams%20of%20protein%20on%20rest%20days%20%E2%80%94%20slightly%20more%20doable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221132%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Protein%20advice%20from%20ChatGPT%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2d3c84d65ec517529e4d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22428%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20started%20snacking%20on%20the%20Greek%20yogurt%20and%20nuts%20in%20the%20office%20instead%20of%20chips.%3Cp%3EChatGPT%2FJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20liked%20when%20ChatGPT%20encouraged%20me%20to%20eat%20more%20food%20and%20make%20more%20helpful%2C%20satiating%20choices%2C%20such%20as%20Greek%20yogurt%20over%20chips.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20also%20appreciated%20that%2C%20even%20though%20I%20forgot%20to%20mention%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-eat-pescatarian-diet-except-when-traveling-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI'm%20a%20pescetarian%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ChatGPT%20seemed%20to%20have%20picked%20up%20on%20my%20habits%20from%20my%20meal%20outlines%2C%20and%20never%20suggested%20products%20like%20meat%20sticks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20protein%20advice%20ChatGPT%20gave%20me%2C%20O'Meara%20said%20the%20tips%20made%20sense.%20%26quot%3BThose%20are%20protein-containing%20foods%2C%20so%20I%20think%20it%20sounds%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20only%20concern%20was%20who%20set%20the%20nutrition%20goal%3A%20a%20professional%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20a%20doctor%2C%20dietitian%2C%20or%20personal%20trainer%20%E2%80%94%20or%20AI%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20hit%20a%20certain%20calorie%20or%20protein%20goal%2C%20just%20make%20sure%20those%20goals%20are%20sound%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22abc87384-943a-4fff-8680-a28687c527fc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20was%20great%20at%20recognizing%20hidden%20eating%20patterns%20that%20made%20it%20harder%20to%20lose%20fat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Salmon%20with%20veggies%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2d46ca7a4f9df67ba3956%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20days%20I%20work%20out%2C%20I%20usually%20eat%20home-cooked%2C%20protein-forward%20meals.%20On%20rest%20days%2C%20not%20so%20much.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20perks%20of%20using%20ChatGPT%20was%20how%20quickly%20it%20identified%20patterns%20in%20my%20eating%2C%20which%20helped%20me%20to%20make%20more%20conscious%20decisions%20around%20my%20meals%20and%20snacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20that%20I%20essentially%20had%20two%20modes.%20Half%20the%20time%2C%20I'd%20finish%20my%20morning%20Orangetheory%20class%2C%20chug%20my%20protein%20shakes%2C%20and%20eat%20my%20meal-prepped%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-high-protein-trader-joes-sheet-pan-dinner-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esheet%20pan%20salmon%20dinners%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20normally%20abstained%20from%20alcohol%20on%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20time%2C%20I'd%20walk%20for%20exercise%20(the%20length%20of%20walking%20greatly%20varying)%2C%20generally%20eat%20less%20protein%2C%20and%20have%20no%20limitations%20at%20dinners%20out.%20I'd%20get%20drinks%2C%20order%20appetizers%2C%20and%20split%20desserts%2C%20feeling%20like%20I'd%20earned%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221394%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ChatGPT%20diet%20patterns%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2d4b5a96e437d6eb83307%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22766%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20needed%20more%20structure%20on%20rest%20days.%3Cp%3EChatGPT%2FJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20taught%20me%20that%20a%20few%20tweaks%20on%20my%20rest%20days%20could%20better%20set%20me%20up%20for%20success.%20It%20suggested%20doing%20more%20steps%2C%20and%20making%20cuts%20to%20help%20achieve%20my%20fat%20loss%20goal%2C%20like%20dialing%20down%20the%20cheese%20in%20salads%20or%20using%20slightly%20less%20peanut%20butter%20in%20my%20morning%20oats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Meara%20said%20noting%20patterns%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-many-calories-should-i-eat-a-day%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsistently%20surpassing%20calorie%20goals%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20course-correct.%20%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20does%20tend%20to%20go%20over%20on%20calories%2C%20limiting%20that%20extra%20stuff%20could%20really%20help%20with%20actually%20getting%20to%20whatever%20your%20calorie%20goals%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20we%20cut%20back%20on%20the%20portion%20sizes%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20have%20to%20totally%20eliminate%20the%20food%20from%20your%20diet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223345%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22pasta%20%2B%20salad%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2dd12a7a4f9df67ba3b17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222509%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChatGPT%20would%20tell%20me%20to%20skip%20the%20cheese.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EO'Meara's%20only%20concern%20was%20that%20AI%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20pattern%2C%20not%20a%20one-off%20indulgent%20dinner%2C%20when%20recommending%20cuts.%20She%20said%20it's%20good%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20how%20often%20you%20overeat%2C%20to%20see%20if%20it's%20a%20pattern%20actually%20worth%20tweaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20the%20issue%20I%20have%20with%20most%20of%20my%20patients%20is%20that%20they%20don't%20eat%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Being%20in%20a%20major%20calorie%20deficit%2C%20such%20as%20eating%20as%20little%20as%201%2C200%20calories%20a%20day%2C%20can%20backfire%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fwhat-is-metabolism%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eslow%20your%20metabolism%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf3a5f78-a409-47f6-be9a-59e7dd81f629%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20of%20the%20tips%20felt%20restrictive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Olive%20oil%20cake%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2dd5aa7a4f9df67ba3b2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20raged%20against%20the%20machine%3A%20I%20had%20a%20dessert%20with%20my%20drink.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20seemed%20to%20give%20me%20trustworthy%20advice.%20It's%20just%20that%20sometimes%20it%20felt%20overwhelming%20to%20hear%20that%2C%20despite%20burning%20538%20calories%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20I%20should%20slow%20down%20on%20the%20goat%20cheese%20in%20my%20grain%20bowl.%20It%20was%20a%20little%20demoralizing%2C%20after%20eating%20the%20majority%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feasy-lunch-grain-bowl-recipe-protein-fiber-dietitian-approved-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprotein-centric%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20home%2C%20that%20I%20should%20feel%20a%20little%20bad%20for%20having%20a%20cocktail%20with%20a%20slice%20of%20cake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20worse%2C%20ChatGPT%20always%20couched%20these%20notes%20with%20lots%20of%20faux%20cheerfulness%2C%20reassuring%20me%20that%20I%20was%20on%20the%20overall%20%26quot%3Bright%20track.%26quot%3B%20It%20felt%20condescending%20after%20being%20told%20to%20not%20%26quot%3Bfree-pour%26quot%3B%20my%20homemade%20salad%20dressing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221286%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ChatGPT%20diet%20advice%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2dfa9a7a4f9df67ba3b9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22838%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20get%20it.%20But%20can%20I%20live%3F%3Cp%3EChatGPT%2FJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20essentially%20a%20robot%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20give%20you%20that%20robot%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Meara%20said.%20Unlike%20a%20dietitian%2C%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20think%20about%20the%20emotional%20benefits%20of%20a%20dinner%20out%20with%20friends%20where%20no%20one%20utters%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bmacros.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnless%20prompted%2C%20it%20might%20also%20give%20you%20more%20restrictions%20than%20swaps.%20A%20dietitian%2C%20O'Meara%20said%2C%20might%20suggest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-cut-drinking-alcohol-one-and-non-rule-mocktails-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20mocktail%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20cutting%20back%20on%20appetizers%20if%20you%20really%20want%20the%20dessert%20and%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20I%20was%20very%20impressed%20with%20how%20easily%20I%20tracked%20my%20eating%20habits%20with%20ChatGPT%2C%20and%20I%20was%20left%20with%20clear%20action%20steps.%20I%20got%20closer%20to%20building%20more%20muscle%20mass%20and%20cutting%20back%20on%20fat%2C%20and%20believe%20the%20habits%20helped%20me%20lose%20a%20pound%20since%20I%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20felt%20like%20a%20computer%20speaking%20to%20another%20computer%2C%20obsessively%20reducing%20my%20life%20to%20calorie%20and%20step%20counts.%20I%20took%20my%20Americanized%20gym%20rat%20lifestyle%20to%20its%20final%20conclusion%2C%20all%20the%20while%20imagining%20a%20chiller%20European%20sitting%20on%20a%20lawn%20somewhere%2C%20laughing%20into%20their%20buttered%20baguette.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20really%20made%20me%20want%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20side%20of%20dessert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fused-chatgpt-track-diet-calories-protein-lose-fat-gain-muscle-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775212261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2e2baa7a4f9df67ba3c24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fused-chatgpt-track-diet-calories-protein-lose-fat-gain-muscle-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20health%20reporter%20told%20ChatGPT%20everything%20she%20ate%20for%20two%20weeks.%20AI%20beat%20food-tracking%20apps%20by%20pointing%20out%20the%20sources%20of%20empty%20calories%2C%20but%20was%20also%20quite%20annoying.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40businessinsider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fused-chatgpt-track-diet-calories-protein-lose-fat-gain-muscle-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Abhishek%20opens%20up%20on%20co-parenting%20with%20Aishwarya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775212248000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129998827%2Cimgsize-32250.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fabhishek-bachchan-opens-up-on-co-parenting-with-aishwarya-rai-bachchan-i-have-never-butted-heads-with-her%2Farticleshow%2F129998827.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129998827.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAb