t%20will%20cost%20%2445%20to%20check%20a%20first%20bag%20if%20you%20pay%20at%20least%2024%20hours%20before%20departure%2C%20per%20its%20website.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJetBlue%20raised%20fees%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20too%2C%20as%20jet%20fuel%20costs%20surge.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funited-airbus-xlr-cabin-premium-economy-business-class-polaris-photos-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnited%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20the%20second%20US%20carrier%20to%20raise%20bag%20fees%20since%20the%20Iran%20war%20sent%20jet%20fuel%20prices%20soaring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20flights%20booked%20from%20Friday%2C%20it%20will%20cost%20%2445%20to%20check%20a%20first%20bag%20if%20you%20pay%20at%20least%2024%20hours%20before%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20check%20a%20bag%20in%20the%20airport%20lobby%2C%20fees%20start%20at%20%2450.%20At%20the%20gate%2C%20it%20will%20cost%20%2475.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20prices%20are%20%2410%20more%20than%20for%20flights%20booked%20before%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnited%20is%20raising%20first%20and%20second%20checked%20bag%20fees%20by%20%2410%20for%20customers%20traveling%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20Canada%20and%20Latin%20America%20beginning%20with%20tickets%20purchased%20Friday%2C%20April%203%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20a%20third%20checked%20bag%20has%20risen%20more%2C%20from%20%24150%20to%20%24200.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjetblue-hikes-checked-bag-fees-citing-rising-operating-costs-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJetBlue%20hiked%20its%20bag%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20by%20between%20%244%20and%20%249%2C%20depending%20on%20whether%20the%20customer%20is%20traveling%20on%20a%20peak%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20experience%20rising%20operating%20costs%2C%20we%20regularly%20evaluate%20how%20to%20manage%20those%20costs%20while%20keeping%20base%20fares%20competitive%20and%20continuing%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20experience%20our%20customers%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20JetBlue%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Iran%20war%20started%20on%20February%2028%2C%20Brent%20Crude%20oil%20prices%20have%20risen%2050%25%20to%20%24109%20a%20barrel.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharts-us-flight-prices-doubled-oil-prices-new-york-london-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejet%20fuel%20has%20surged%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20more.%20It's%20doubled%20in%20price%20to%20almost%20%24200%20a%20barrel%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20International%20Air%20Transport%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20airlines%20around%20the%20world%2C%20US%20carriers%20don't%20hedge%20against%20fuel%20costs%2C%20so%20they%20face%20greater%20risk%20from%20rising%20prices.%20Meanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-ceo-warns-25-percent-jet-fuel-threatened-iran-war-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEurope's%20biggest%20airline%2C%20Ryanair%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20locked%20in%20lower%20fuel%20prices%20for%2080%25%20of%20its%20supply%20until%20next%20March%2C%20its%20CEO%20told%20Sky%20News%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20JetBlue%20has%20also%20led%20the%20way%20in%20raising%20bag%20fees%2C%20with%20competitors%20following.%20Back%20in%202018%2C%20it%20was%20the%20first%20major%20airline%20to%20start%20charging%20%2430%20for%20a%20checked%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlaska%20Airlines%20and%20JetBlue%20kicked%20off%20the%20last%20round%20of%20bag%20fee%20increases%20in%20early%202024.%20United%20and%20most%20other%20carriers%20then%20raised%20their%20prices%20by%20%245.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnited%20Chase%20credit%20card%20holders%2C%20MileagePlus%20Premier%20members%2C%20active%20military%20members%2C%20and%20customers%20