ms%2C%20including%20The%20Carlyle%20Group%20and%20Dalfen%20Industrial%2C%20which%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dalfen.com%2Fnews%2Fgoldman-venture-buys-300-million-of-warehouses-from-blackstone%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520bank%2520partnered%2520with%2520Dallas%252Dbased%2CCincinnati%2520and%2520parts%2520of%2520Pennsylvania.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epartnership%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20every%20seller%20purchased%20the%20land%20and%20built%20the%20warehouses%20within%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20flipping%20or%20leasing%20them%20to%20an%20e-commerce%20or%20logistics%20company%2C%20according%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20review%20of%20public%20records%2C%20news%20reports%2C%20press%20releases%2C%20and%20commercial%20real%20estate%20listings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Blue%20Owl%20sold%20a%20Tremont%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20facility%20to%20ICE%20for%20%24119%20million.%20A%20private%20credit%20firm%20that%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-owl-ai-infrastructure-investments-loans-equity-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrawn%20scrutiny%20for%20its%20participation%20in%20the%20AI%20data%20center%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Blue%20Owl%20purchased%20the%20warehouse%2C%20a%20former%20Big%20Lots%20distribution%20center%2C%20for%20%24129.5%20million%20from%20the%20retailer%20in%202020.%20It%20was%20leasing%20it%20back%20to%20Big%20Lots%20when%20the%20company%20went%20bankrupt%20four%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20warehouse%2C%20which%20ICE%20told%20city%20officials%20could%20hold%20up%20to%2010%2C000%20people%20at%20a%20time%2C%20is%20located%20in%20a%20heavily%20industrialized%20area%20near%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20International%20Airport%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.loopnet.com%2FListing%2F6020-W-300-S-Salt-Lake-City-UT%2F21458937%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistribution%20centers%20for%20retailers%20like%20Amazon%20and%20Sephora%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20funds%20for%20the%20acquisitions%2C%20which%20the%20White%20House%20said%20will%20support%20a%20daily%20detention%20capacity%20of%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%20100%2C000%20aliens%2C%26quot%3B%20are%20coming%20from%20federal%20tax%20dollars%20allocated%20in%20last%20summer's%20Big%20Beautiful%20Bill%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20buildings%20is%20a%20new%20strategy%20for%20ICE%2C%20which%20has%20historically%20leased%20its%20detention%20facilities%20from%20private%20prison%20firms.%20This%20new%20approach%20is%20meant%20to%20rapidly%20add%20more%20beds%20and%20streamline%20the%20agency's%20deportation%20operations%2C%20according%20to%20an%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.governor.nh.gov%2Fsites%2Fg%2Ffiles%2Fehbemt971%2Ffiles%2Finline-documents%2Fmerrimack-detention-reengineering-initiative-3.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edocument%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20by%20New%20Hampshire%20Gov.%20Kelly%20Ayotte.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ICE%20warehouse%20Romulus%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd800cc02a678bd7e471e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProtestors%20outside%20a%20warehouse%20in%20suburban%20Detroit%2C%20Michigan.%3Cp%3E%3A%20Jim%20West%2FUCG%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20says%20ICE%20believes%20the%20renovation%20of%20%26quot%3Bnon-traditional%26quot%3B%20facilities%20will%20allow%20it%20to%20quickly%20build%20new%20detention%20centers%20that%20are%20customized%20to%20the%20agency's%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fimmigration%2F2026%2F03%2F27%2Finternal-memos-hint-mullins-first-changes-dhs-secretary%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENews%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20suggest%20that%20ICE's%20plans%20for%20its%20detention%20centers%20will%20be%20paused%20while%20new%20Secretary%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20Markwayne%20Mullins%20reviews%20former%20Secretary%20Kristi%20Noem's%20policies%20after%20she%20was%20removed%20from%20her%20post%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EICE%20previously%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20acquire%2024%20properties%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mix%20of%2016%20regional%20processing%20centers%2C%20meant%20to%20house%20up%20to%201%2C500%20people%20for%20up%20to%20a%20week%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20eight%20%26quot%3Blarge-scale%26quot%3B%20detention%20centers%20meant%20to%20hold%207%2C000%20to%2010%2C000%20people%20for%20one%20to%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20it%20aimed%20to%20have%20the%20facilities%20operational%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EICE's%20warehouse%20plans%20have%20faced%20public%20pushback%20in%20some%20communities%2C%20leading%20some%20warehouse%20owners%20in%20other%20locations%20to%20cancel%20previously%20planned%20sales%20to%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Merrillville%2C%20Indiana%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20warehouse%20thought%20to%20be%20under%20consideration%20for%20sale%20to%20ICE%20issued%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2Fh9KaE%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20stating%20that%20it%20was%20not%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fksltv.com%2Flocal-news%2Fwarehouse-salt-lake-protest%2F889945%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotest%3C%2Fa%3E%20outside%20a%20warehouse%20in%20Salt%20Lake%20City%2C%20a%20man%20was%20arrested%20on%20a%20charge%20of%20property%20damage%20after%20police%20found%20him%20inside%20the%20building%2C%20throwing%20rocks%20at%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fice-buying-warehouses-to-make-detention-centers-2026-4%5C%22%3EBu