epreneurial%20journey%20handing%20out%20flyers%20in%20my%20neighborhood%20of%20Hollis%2C%20Queens%2C%20for%20%242%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20grade%20school%2C%20I%20scraped%20the%20paint%20off%20pencils%20and%20customized%20them%20with%20the%20customer's%20name%20for%20a%20fee.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaymond-john-red-lobster-2015-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20waited%20tables%20at%20Red%20Lobster%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20around%20the%20time%20I%20told%20my%20mother%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20an%20apparel%20company%20for%20young%20men%2C%20so%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshark-tanks-daymond-john-mother-2015-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20taught%20me%20to%20sew%20wool%20caps%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daymond%20John%20poses%20in%20New%20York%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd6e17c02a678bd7e47108%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226240%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20in%20New%20York.%3Cp%3EThe%20Shark%20Group%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20cheap%20fabric%2C%20sewed%2080%20of%20them%2C%20and%20sold%20them%20for%20%2410%20a%20pop%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fjamesaltucher.com%2F2016%2F01%2Fdaymond-john-schools-me-on-the-power-of-broke%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearned%20me%20%24800%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpower-hours-day-in-the-life-successful-business-leaders-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPower%20Hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20series%20gives%20readers%20an%20inside%20look%20at%20how%20powerful%20leaders%20in%20business%20structure%20their%20workday.%20Reach%20out%20to%20editor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Flauryn-haas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELauryn%20Haas%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20share%20your%20daily%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20seeing%20how%20much%20I%20thrived%20at%20it%2C%20my%20mom%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshark-tanks-daymond-john-mother-2015-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emortgaged%20her%20home%20to%20raise%20%24100%2C000%20to%20fund%20my%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20officially%20launched%20in%201992.%20I%20set%20up%20in%20her%20house%2C%20splitting%20my%20time%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffubu.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFUBU%3C%2Fa%3E%20(For%20Us%2C%20By%20Us)%20and%20Red%20Lobster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20had%20enough%20money%20to%20quit%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20the%20business%20my%20full%20attention%20%E2%80%94%20I%20quit%20Red%20Lobster%20around%201995%20and%20went%20completely%20full-time%20with%20FUBU.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20turned%20a%20small%20operation%20based%20out%20of%20my%20mom's%20home%20into%20a%20booming%20business%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaymond-john-explains-why-being-broke-was-key-to-his-success-2016-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerating%20%24350%20million%20in%20revenue%20within%20six%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20I%20run%20three%20businesses%3A%20FUBU%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesharkgroup.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20brand%20management%20agency%20called%20The%20Shark%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20coworking%20space%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdaymondjohn.com%2Fblogs%2Fnews%2Fdaymond-john-unveils-new-coworking-space-blueprint-and-co%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlueprint%20%2B%20co%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%2014%20seasons%20of%20Shark%20Tank%2C%20I've%20also%20invested%20in%20over%2030%20brands%20across%20various%20industries%20as%20a%20Shark.%20I'm%20a%20father%20of%20three%2C%20with%20one%20still%20at%20home%2C%20and%20I%20travel%20250%20days%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20a%20typical%20day%20looks%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22199d89e5-5701-4436-8d16-33c168c54277%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20wake%20up%20around%206%3A15%20a.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20wake%20up%2C%20I%20don't%20rush%20to%20grab%20my%20phone%2C%20but%20I%20do%20glance%20at%20it%20to%20make%20sure%20there%20are%20no%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20fast%2C%20drink%20water%20and%20coffee%2C%20and%20don't%20eat%20breakfast%3B%20I%20only%20eat%20between%202%20p.m.%20and%208%20p.m.%20Once%20a%20week%2C%20I%20fast%20for%2024%20to%2036%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it's%20a%20weekday%2C%20I%20take%20my%209-year-old%20daughter%20to%20school%2C%20and%20then%20I%20walk%20for%20about%20an%20hour%20to%20my%20office%20in%20Miami.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225151%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daymond%20John%20poses%20in%20a%20white%20outfit%20in%20Miami%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd4ce0e762ed6cfe449453%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223864%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20in%20Miami.%3Cp%3EThe%20Shark%20Group%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20big%20into%20fitness%20and%20longevity%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20personal%20trainer.%20I%20do%20explosive%20exercises%20whenever%20I%20can%2C%20once%20a%20day%20for%2015%20to%2020%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20anything%20from%20squats%20to%20box%20jumps%20to%20push-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e36a9401-7dee-4352-8ee7-471126cedfe7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20like%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%20between%209%20a.m.%20and%2010%20a.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20travel%20250%20days%20a%20year%2C%20so%20my%20morning%20routine%20is%20not%20every%20day.%20When%20I'm%20not%20traveling%2C%20I%20prefer%20to%20go%20to%20my%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20often%20have%20to%20rush%20right%20into%20meetings%20when%20I%20start%20working%2C%20since%20I'm%20on%20the%20road%20so%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20morning%20is%20stacked%20with%20faculty%20meetings.%20I'll%20work%20until%20my%20eating%20window%2C%20starting%20at%202%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2244de01a8-f561-46e7-a14d-38da5eb358a2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20take%20a%20formal%20lunch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20do%20eat%20at%202%20p.m.%2C%20I%20have%20something%20brought%20into%20my%20office%20while%20I'm%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tend%20to%20eat%20some%20form%20of%20protein%2C%20whether%20it's%20fish%20or%20beef%2C%20and%20fresh%20produce%2C%20while%20avoiding%20processed%20foods%20and%20alcohol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20coffee%20drinker%2C%20and%20I'll%20have%20three%20cold-brew%20coffees%20throughout%20the%20day.%20I%20also%20drink%20plenty%20of%20water%2C%20unsweetened%20iced%20tea%2C%20and%20an%20all-natural%20energy%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e78e3c0-8936-4c41-a450-bbbc9da52a69%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20have%20a%20great%20routine%2C%20but%20my%20day%20can%20be%20derailed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20meetings%20I%20have%20throughout%20the%20day%20are%20for%20my%20companies%2C%20the%20companies%20I've%20invested%20in%2C%20and%20everything%20in%20between.%20Derailing%20can%20occur%20if%20a%20meeting%20is%20poorly%20structured%20or%20runs%20longer%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwice%20a%20month%2C%20for%20about%20six%20hours%2C%20I%20meet%20the%20founders%20of%20companies%20I've%20invested%20in.%20My%20afternoon%20is%20like%20the%20morning%20%E2%80%94%20full%20of%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c4367ce-3498-4ab8-9bf5-680623c020d5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20try%20to%20get%20home%20every%20day%20by%207%3A30%20p.m.%20to%20put%20my%20daughter%20to%20bed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22head%20shot%20of%20Daymond%20John%20sitting%20on%20stairs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd6f016a864f6fcd7bc757%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn.%3Cp%3EThe%20Shark%20Group%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20get%20my%20daughter%20down%20for%20the%20night%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20catch%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20dinner%2C%20a%20chef%20comes%20by%20and%20delivers%20food%20to%20our%20home%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20week.%20The%20meal%20is%20similar%20to%20lunch%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20protein%20and%20fresh%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20go%20into%20some%20longevity%20routines%2C%20as%20I'm%20passionate%20about%20them.%20I%20have%20a%20house%20full%20of%20biohacking%20machines%2C%20so%20I'll%20lie%20in%20a%20red%20bed%20or%20an%20electric%20mat.%20I%20regularly%20do%20cold%20punges%20and%20take%20my%20workouts%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20watch%20TV%20unless%20it's%20financial%20news%20running%20in%20the%20background.%20I%20listen%20to%20podcasts%20and%20read%20motivational%20or%20longevity-%20and%20biohacking-related%20books%2C%20such%20as%20Gary%20Brecka%2C%20Joe%20Rogan%2C%20and%20Dave%20Asprey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e9779bf-a9e4-491e-8fc1-43d75713f1b8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20get%20to%20bed%20around%2010%3A30%20p.m.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBiohacking%2C%20longevity%2C%20and%20trying%20to%20be%20healthier%20and%20live%20longer%20are%20a%20focus%20in%20my%20life%20at%2057%20years%20old%20because%20I%20want%20to%20reduce%20potential%20cancers%2C%20infections%2C%20and%20inflammation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20faced%20cancer%20in%202017%2C%20but%20after%20I%20beat%20it%2C%20I%20still%20didn't%20make%20the%20necessary%20changes%20to%20my%20lifestyle.%20It%20wasn't%20until%20around%202022%20that%20I%20started%20changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20taking%20it%20seriously%20because%20I%20have%20a%20significant%20other%20who's%20always%20making%20sure%20she%20takes%20care%20of%20her%20health%2C%20fitness%2C%20and%20diet.%20I%20stopped%20drinking%20alcohol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20love%20to%20get%206.5%20hours%20of%20sleep%2C%20but%20I%20generally%20don't%2C%20so%20I%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20naps%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20sometimes%20in%20the%20office%2C%20and%20I%20nap%20on%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20probably%20don't%20fall%20asleep%20until%2011%3A30%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2283071630-a42c-461f-b5c6-d56ed37764e6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20have%20a%20few%20other%20passions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20an%20avid%20fisherman%20and%20unwind%20by%20spending%20time%20with%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20to%20give%20artists%20access%20to%20my%20public%20stage%20so%20they%20can%20create%20more%20art.%20I%20also%20like%20live%20selling%2C%20whether%20it's%20vending%20machines%20(I've%20just%20launched%20some)%20or%20selling%20on%20platforms%20like%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestments%20dovetail%20into%20every%20part%20of%20my%20career%2C%20including%20investments%20in%20AI%20companies%20such%20as%20Lotus%20AI.%20And%20then%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Shark%20Tank%20and%20all%20my%20investments%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20film%20on%20Shark%20Tank%2C%20shooting%20two%20pods%20a%20year%2C%20each%20about%20two%20weeks.%20I'm%20not%20shooting%20every%20one%20of%20those%2014%20days%2C%20but%20they%20are%20on%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20people%20would%20be%20surprised%20by%20how%20very%20busy%20my%20schedule%20is%20and%20how%20little%20time%20there%20is%20to%20breathe%2C%20which%20is%20a%20problem.%20I'm%20always%20trying%20to%20figure%20things%20out%3B%20it's%20just%20nonstop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaymond-john-fubu-shark-tank-power-hours-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775207101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69cd4b646a864f6fcd7bc5df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaymond