5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EConsulting%20firms%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20streamline%20operations%20by%20reducing%20management%20layers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20is%20helping%20leaders%20manage%20larger%20teams%20and%20improve%20decision-making.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECompanies%20like%20IBM%20and%20Factory%20are%20also%20adopting%20AI%20to%20reshape%20management%20structures.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20consulting%20firms%2C%20shredding%20season%20is%20coming%3A%20It's%20time%20to%20take%20AI%20and%20cut%20the%20fat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20companies%20embed%20AI%20agents%20into%20their%20workflows%2C%20consultants%20are%20exploring%20how%20it%20can%20be%20used%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-agents-management-structure-org-chart-consulting-firms-mckinsey-ibm-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflatten%20management%20layers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20helping%20leaders%20oversee%20increasingly%20wider%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-new-partners-advice-tips-consulting-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMcKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%3C%2Fa%3E%20senior%20partner%20Alexis%20Krivkovich%20said%20there's%20%26quot%3Breal%20hope%26quot%3B%20that%20AI%20can%20help%20companies%20streamline%20their%20organizational%20structures%20during%20a%20recent%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20McKinsey%20Podcast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20equipped%20leaders%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Bmore%20of%20a%20superhuman%20capacity%20to%20manage%20across%20bigger%20scopes%2C%20which%20would%20allow%20companies%20to%20flatten%20their%20structure%20and%20get%20faster%20in%20the%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20she%20said%2C%20companies%20have%20inserted%20at%20least%20one%20organizational%20layer%20in%20their%20management%20structure%20between%20the%20CEO%20and%20the%20front%20line.%20In%20some%2C%20it%20has%20been%20closer%20to%20two%20or%20three%20layers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20is%20that%20expensive%2C%20but%20that%20slows%20companies%20down%20from%20a%20decision-making%20standpoint%20because%20it%20just%20means%20you%20have%20more%20people%2C%20more%20layers%20at%20which%20somebody%20has%20to%20weigh%20in%20before%20any%20decision%20can%20get%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%2C%20instead%2C%20can%20be%20used%20to%20facilitate%20decisions%20and%20connection%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20organizations%20will%20change%20is%20likely%20to%20vary%20from%20industry%20to%20industry.%20In%20the%20life%20sciences%2C%20%26quot%3Bsquads%20of%20agents%26quot%3B%20can%20supercharge%20innovation.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20AI%20agents%20can%20automate%20work%20in%20departments%20like%20human%20resources%2C%20finance%2C%20and%20legal%2C%20and%20even%20reallocate%20resources%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20business%2C%20Krivkovich%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20have%20dubbed%20this%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-flattening-middle-managers-performance-efficiency-ai-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20Great%20Flattening%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20restructuring%20of%20corporate%20hierarchies%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20org%20chart%20is%20probably%20going%20to%20start%20condensing%20into%20becoming%20more%20flat%20horizontally%2C%26quot%3B%20Eno%20Reyes%2C%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Factory%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFactory%20is%20an%20AI-native%20software%20development%20platform%20that%20builds%20and%20deploys%20autonomous%20coding%20agents%20for%20consulting%20firms%20like%20EY%20and%20companies%20like%20Nvidia%20and%20Adobe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20IBM%2C%20too%2C%20which%20has%20its%20own%20consulting%20arm%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20Mohamed%20Ali%20expects%20new%20management%20structures%20to%20emerge%20as%20it%20embeds%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20workers%26quot%3B%20alongside%20its%20150%2C000%20human%20consultants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20human%20managers%20are%20going%20to%20manage%20these%20things%20in%20the%20same%20way%20as%20we%20manage%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Ali%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThere'll%20be%20systems%20to%20manage%20these%20things.%20There'll%20be%20systems%20to%20set%20up%20the%20guardrails.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-ai-agents-mangement-leadership-great-flattening-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775207041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab1103d3e2f1aef36a236d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-ai-agents-mangement-leadership-great-flattening-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22McKinsey%20and%20other%20consulting%20firms%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20streamline%20management%20structures%20%E2%80%94%20what%20some%20call%20The%20Great%20Flattening.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-ai-agents-mangement-leadership-great-flattening-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sonam%20shares%20first%20PHOTO%20with%20her%20newborn%20from%20the%20hospital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775206863000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129997725%2Cimgsize-33904.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsonam-kapoor-shares-first-heartwarming-photo-with-her-newborn-from-the-hospital-see-photo%2Farticleshow%2F129997725.cms%