ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspace-stock-spacex-ipo-valuation-elon-musk-rklb-asts-star-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpaceX%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E%20excitement%20to%20Nvidia's%20foray%20into%20space%20computing%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-centers-in-space-google-moonshot-project-suncatcher-tesla-openai-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edata%20centers%20in%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20become%20the%20tech%20industry's%20new%20favorite%20talking%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20economy%20could%20become%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mckinsey.com%2Ffeatured-insights%2Fthemes%2Fthe-space-economy-is-projected-to-reach-1-8-trillion-by-2035%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241.8%20trillion%20opportunity%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%202035%2C%20according%20to%20consulting%20firm%20McKinsey%20and%20Company.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20while%20some%20major%20companies%20are%20ready%20to%20spend%20billions%20launching%20GPU-loaded%20satellites%20into%20orbit%2C%20not%20everyone%20on%20this%20planet%20is%20buying%20in%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20leaders%20like%20SpaceX%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-hiring-elon-musk-data-centers-in-space-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Amazon%20founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-tera-wave-blue-origin-elon-musk-spacex-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJeff%20Bezos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Google%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-project-suncatcher-sundar-pichai-data-centers-space-solar-2027-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESundar%20Pichai%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20framing%20data%20centers%20in%20space%20as%20a%20cost-effective%20solution%20to%20AI's%20insatiable%20appetite%20for%20resources%2C%20such%20as%20land%20and%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGlobal%20electricity%20demand%20for%20AI%20simply%20cannot%20be%20met%20with%20terrestrial%20solutions%2C%20even%20in%20the%20near%20term%2C%20without%20imposing%20hardship%20on%20communities%20and%20the%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20wrote%20in%20a%20February%20post%20on%20SpaceX's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProponents%20of%20data%20centers%20in%20space%20make%20a%20simple%20case.%20Space%20data%20centers%20can%20get%20free%20power%20from%20the%20sun%20and%20don't%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20real%20estate%20%E2%80%94%20and%20best%20of%20all%2C%20both%20resources%20are%20unlimited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20space%20is%20called%20'space'%20for%20a%20reason%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20wrote%20on%20the%20company%20site%2C%20adding%20in%20a%20laughing-crying%20emoji.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20wary%20of%20data%20centers%20in%20space%20say%20the%20endeavor%20is%20far%20more%20technically%20complicated%2C%20cumbersome%2C%20and%20expensive%20than%20it%20might%20appear.%20OpenAI%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-elon-musk-data-centers-space-timeline-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20also%20called%20the%20idea%20%26quot%3Bridiculous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20wild%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kathleen%20Curlee%2C%20a%20space%20economy%20research%20analyst%20at%20Georgetown's%20Center%20for%20Security%20and%20Emerging%20Technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20put%20a%20data%20center%20in%20space.%20It%20is%20not%20physically%20impossible%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Matthew%20Buckley%2C%20a%20theoretical%20physicist%20and%20associate%20professor%20at%20Rutgers%20University's%20department%20of%20physics%20and%20astronomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20don't%20see%20why%20you%20would%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc42f7db-c66f-47f5-a863-a0e976c414e7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETech%20giants%20like%20SpaceX%20and%20Google%20see%20big%20opportunities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20isn't%20alone%20in%20his%20dreams%20of%20orbital%20data%20centers.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-data-center-space-solar-power-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20Project%20Suncatcher%3C%2Fa%3E%20aims%20to%20deploy%20an%20AI%20data%20center%20in%20low%20Earth%20orbit%20by%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Blue%20Origin%2C%20the%20space%20technology%20company%20founded%20by%20Bezos%2C%20asked%20the%20federal%20government%20for%20permission%20to%20launch%20a%20network%20of%2050%2C000%20solar-powered%20data%20center%20satellites%20into%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20application%2C%20Blue%20Origin%20wrote%20that%20moving%20data%20centers%20into%20space%20would%20help%20ease%20the%20pressure%20on%20US%20communities%20and%20natural%20resources%20from%20energy-%20and%20%26quot%3Bwater-intensive%20compute.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226483%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Google%20data%20center%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ced99ee762ed6cfe449d7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224322%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20has%20been%20scaling%20out%20its%20AI%20data%20centers%20on%20land%2C%20and%20it%20also%20has%20plans%20to%20deploy%20data%20centers%20to%20space.%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Johnson%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Nvidia%20launched%20hardware%20for%20data%20centers%20in%20space.%20The%20company's%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-space-data-centers-ai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJensen%20Huang%20%3C%2Fa%3Esaid%20in%20February%20that%20the%20economics%20of%20data%20centers%20in%20space%20%26quot%3Bwill%20improve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20can't%20seem%20to%20get%20enough%20of%20data%20centers%20in%20space%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeattle-based%20space%20data%20center%20startup%20Starcloud%20announced%20this%20week%20that%20it%20had%20reached%20a%20%241.1%20billion%20valuation%20following%20a%20%24170%20million%20Series%20A%20round%20led%20by%20Benchmark%20and%20EQT%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarcloud%20reached%20unicorn%20status%20faster%20than%20any%20other%20startup%20to%20ever%20come%20out%20of%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobinhood%20cofounder%20Baiju%20Bhatt%2C%20who%20became%20a%20billionaire%20when%20the%20stock-trading%20app%20went%20public%20in%202021%2C%20began%20investing%20in%20space%20data%20centers%20in%202024.%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%20that%20his%20space%20solar%20power%20company%2C%20Aetherflux%2C%20is%20raising%20a%20new%20round%20of%20funding%20at%20a%20%242%20billion%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb5b6414-6098-4f7e-b5f9-e97a140dbfee%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpace%20data%20centers%20have%20hidden%20costs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20cited%20a%20litany%20of%20obstacles%20that%20space-based%20data%20centers%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuckley%2C%20the%20theoretical%20physicist%2C%20estimated%20that%20every%20data%20center%20launched%20into%20space%20would%20require%20450%20football%20fields%20of%20solar%20panels%20to%20power%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20alone%20could%20cost%20%2410%20billion%20per%20data%20center%2C%20he%20estimated%2C%20on%20top%20of%20an%20additional%20%2410%20billion%20to%20launch%20it%20into%20orbit%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20not%20counting%20the%20cost%20of%20maintaining%20the%20data%20center%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20center%20maintenance%20in%20space%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20complicated%20than%20maintenance%20on%20Earth%2C%20Curlee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20the%20issue%20of%20space%20debris%20%E2%80%94%20they%20could%20get%20hit%20with%20a%20fleck%20of%20paint%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20sustain%20damage%20or%20go%20offline%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20this%2C%20space%20data%20centers%20aren't%20meant%20to%20last%20very%20long%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20a%20maximum%20of%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20amount%20it%20would%20take%20to%20get%20data%20centers%20into%20space%20isn't%20justifiable%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20long-term%20goal%20being%20presented%20as%20if%20it%20could%20be%20achieved%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-jeff-bezos-space-data-centers-scientists-ask-why-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775206804000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ced2446a864f6fcd7bcec6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-jeff-bezos-space-data-centers-scientists-ask-why-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tech%20billionaires%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Jeff%20Bezos%20are%20advocating%20for%20space%20data%20centers%20to%20scale%20AI.%20Scientists%20say%20it%20can%20get%20expensive%20fast.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ellen%20Thomas)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-jeff-bezos-space-data-centers-scientists-ask-why-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Smita%20Patil%20wanted%20to%20go%20as%20a%20'suhagan'%2C%20Big%20B%20%26amp%3Bamp%3B%20others%20were%20present%20at%20her%20funeral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1775206545000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129997636%2Cimgsize-25062.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsmita-patil-wanted-to-go-as-a-suhagan-when-she-died-amitabh-bachchan-and-others-were-present-at-her-funeral-i-cried-and-did-her-make-up%2Far